License-file: LICENSE

Author: Brett Letner <brettletner@gmail.com>

Maintainer: Brett Letner <brettletner@gmail.com>

Copyright: Brett letner 2011

Category: Language

Build-type: Simple

Extra-source-files: Pec.cf

